name: Metaphys Ragnarok
desc: If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can banish 3 cards from the top of your Deck, and if you do, this card gains 300 ATK for each "Metaphys" card banished by this effect, except "Metaphysical Regeneration". When this card inflicts battle damage to your opponent: You can Special Summon 1 Level 5 or higher "Metaphys" monster from your Deck, but banish it during the End Phase of next turn. You can only use each effect of "Metaphys Ragnarok" once per turn.
